<!DOCTYPE HTML>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>Pharmacy Recommendation</title>
    <link rel="icon" href="/favicon.ico" type="image/x-icon">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/lib/bootstrap.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.15.3/css/all.min.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@300;400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
            background: url('/images/pharm.png') no-repeat center center fixed;
            background-size: cover;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 630px;
        }
        .main-header {
            background-color: rgba(107, 170, 117, 0.9);
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .main-header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 2.2rem;
            text-shadow: 1px 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            white-space: nowrap;
            overflow: hidden;
            text-overflow: ellipsis;
        }
        .main-body {
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
            border-radius: 0 0 10px 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .lead {
            font-weight: 400;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
        }
        .lead span {
            color: #6BAA75;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        .form-control-lg {
            border: 2px solid #6BAA75;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 15px;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }
        .form-control-lg::placeholder {
            color: #aaa;
        }
        .btn-success {
            background-color: #6BAA75;
            border-color: #6BAA75;
            font-weight: 500;
            padding: 12px 20px;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            border-radius: 10px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        .btn-success:hover, .btn-success:focus {
            background-color: #5a9164;
            border-color: #5a9164;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        @media (max-width: 576px) {
            .main-header h1 {
                font-size: 1.8rem;
            }
            .lead {
                font-size: 1rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
    <div class="main-header">
        <h1><i class="fas fa-pills mr-2"></i> 약국 추천 </h1>
    </div>
    <div class="main-body">
        <p class="lead">주소를 입력하시면 <span>가까운 약국의 위치 최대 3곳</span>을 추천해 드립니다.</p>
        <form action="/search" method="post">
            <div class="mb-3">
                <input type="text" class="form-control form-control-lg" id="address_kakao" name="address"
                       placeholder="주소(지번 또는 도로명)를 입력하세요. ex) 서울특별시 성북구 종암로 10길">
            </div>
            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-success btn-lg btn-block">
                <i class="fas fa-search mr-2"></i> Search
            </button>
        </form>
    </div>
</div>

<script src="/js/lib/jquery.min.js"></script>
<script src="/js/lib/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
<script src="//t1.daumcdn.net/mapjsapi/bundle/postcode/prod/postcode.v2.js"></script>
<script>
    window.onload = function() {
        document.getElementById("address_kakao").addEventListener("click", function(){
            new daum.Postcode({
                oncomplete: function(data) {
                    document.getElementById("address_kakao").value = data.address;
                }
            }).open();
        });
    }
</script>
</body>
</html>